headline: Uber Eats launches partnership with Family Dollar
summary: Uber Technologies (UBER) announced the launch of a new partnership with Family Dollar (DLTR), bringing its broad selection of affordable household items to Uber Eats. With more than 5,000 Family Dollar locations now live on Uber Eats across the U.S., customers can shop for a wide variety of everyday items-from cleaning supplies and pantry staples to beauty products and baby care-delivered directly to their door, on-demand or scheduled. To mark this launch, Uber Eats is offering 40% off of orders
